snippet.title: Official Trailer: Rise of the Sky Eater l Skylanders Superchargers l Skylanders
snippet.description:
In Skylanders® SuperChargers, Kaos has unleashed his most evil monstrosity yet—the SKY EATER! But the Skylanders can’t stop him alone. They’ll need an unstoppable fleet of amazing new vehicles. And one other thing… help from a portal master like YOU! Now is the time. Drive evil crazy!
#superchargers
SUBSCRIBE: https://www.youtube.com/user/skylandersgame?sub_confirmation=1

Twitter: https://twitter.com/skylandersgame

About Skylanders Superchargers: 
Skylands is in peril! Kaos has unleashed his most evil weapon yet – the Doomstation of Ultimate Doomstruction. With all of Skylands on the verge of collapse, a special team called the SuperChargers has been assembled to pilot an unstoppable fleet of incredible vehicles. Now you and the SuperChargers must embark on epic adventures over land, under sea, and through the sky to stop Kaos and save Skylands!
